@META
dir: skillsPraut/src/components/transitions
updated: 2026-04-15
files: 9
stack: React, Remotion, TypeScript

@EXPORTS
FadeTransition.tsx: FadeTransition — fade in/out wrapper using springs.smooth
GlitchTransition.tsx: GlitchTransition — RGB-split glitch for durationFrames
MorphTransition.tsx: MorphTransition — cross-fade morph between two children (opacity + blur)
ParticleBurst.tsx: ParticleBurst — radial particle burst from center (purple/blue)
PuzzleAssemble.tsx: PuzzleAssemble — 4 puzzle tiles slide into brain mark + "CX" badge
RippleEffect.tsx: RippleEffect — concentric expanding rings from center
SlideTransition.tsx: SlideTransition — directional slide using springs.snappy
WipeTransition.tsx: WipeTransition — purple gradient mask sweep reveal
ZoomTransition.tsx: ZoomTransition — scale-zoom using springs.smooth

@INTERFACES
CommonTransitionProps: { children, startFrame?, durationFrames? }
FadeTransitionProps: { ...CommonTransitionProps, direction?: "in"|"out" }

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: styles/tokens (colors, springs, timing, glow, fonts)
external: remotion (AbsoluteFill, spring, interpolate, useCurrentFrame, useVideoConfig)

@STANDARDS
- All transitions accept startFrame + durationFrames props
- Default duration: timing.medium (24 frames / 0.8s)
- PuzzleAssemble is the signature Praut brand transition
- PuzzleAssemble tiles: #506FFB at 100/70/45/25% opacity
- Deterministic seeded random for ParticleBurst
